Subprog AS_CLLCVT(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(44763,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
## Action DEFHRCLV
Call DEFHRCLV(VALEUR,GCURLEG,GSOCIETE) From SUBHRCLV
If mkstat=2
 [M]CLLCVT(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo CLLCVT(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_CLLCVT(zc) From W1FCYPAY
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_CLLCVT(zc) From W1FCYPAY
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_CLLCVT(zc) From W1FCYPAY
